<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>org.adjam.cutepad</id>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">cutepad.desktop</launchable>
  <name>Cutepad</name>
  <summary>Lightweight Qt plain text editor</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0</project_license>
  <description>
    <p>Cutepad is a lightweight plain-text editor based on Qt. Its main features are:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Syntax highlighting (thanks to the magical KF5::syntaxhighlightning library</li>
      <li>Option to show line numbers</li>
      <li>Option to highlight current line</li>
      <li>Tab/Space replacement</li>
      <li>Printing</li>
      <li>Text zooming</li>
      <li>Ability to work in fullscreen mode</li>
      <li>Find and replace widgets</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
